      <title>美国衰退恐惧为债券投资者带来“灰色天鹅”的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-recession-worries-raise-gray-swan-risk-for-bond-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者对全球信贷进行了为期一年的集会，这是因为美国政策不确定性使世界上最大的经济体陷入经济衰退的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-recession-worries-raise-gray-swan-risk-for-bond-investors</guid>
